name: Go Emoji Go The Maze
description:
Cool 😎 Emoji Has Stolen The 12 All Seeing Oracle Pyramids From RoboLand And He Has Escaped To His Home Planet Of Emojiville. The Intergalactic Federation Has Called Upon GoBot Jr As The Protector Of The Universe To Retrieve The Stolen Oracle Pyramids.

Can You Help GoBot Jr Complete His Mission?

Game Strategies:

  • Use Jump Button To Look Over Walls And Find Your Location In The Maze.
  • Use Portals To Find Shortcuts Through The Maze.
  • Avoid All Emojis And Bombs.

HINT:

All Levels Pop Up At Random. If You Find Yourself Stuck On A Level You Can Press The Exit Button And Restart The Game And You'll Be On A New Level.
